title: UCD SNMP Daemon: DiskIO
agents: snmp
catalog: os/storage
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the disk IO for systems running the UCD SNMP daemon.
 This daemon is mostly found on Linux systems and used by some hardware
 appliances (such as Riverbed Steelhead or EMC ECS).
 'Levels for disk IO' can be used to set thresholds for read/write.

item:
 Index of the disk

discovery:
 One service is created for each disk.
